dct_title_s: Plan der Altstadt von Nürnberg : Plan of the old town.
dct_description_sm: Some buildings shown in pictorial relief.   Indexed.   North oriented to the upper right.   Includes ill. and advertisements.   On verso: advertisements and ancillary maps: Pleasure resorts, parks in and near Nuremberg -- Interesting excursions from Nuremberg.
